-- European Stocks Advance as BP Surges to One-Month High; Stoxx 600 Climbs
-- Andrew Rummer
-- 2010-07-13T07:14:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-13/european-stocks-advance-as-bp-surges-to-one-month-high-stoxx-600-climbs.html

          
          
             European stocks advanced for a sixth
day as BP Plc rallied to a one-month high after installing a new
cap on its leaking Gulf of Mexico oil well.  
 The Stoxx Europe 600 Index rose 0.3 percent to 251.94 at
8:13 a.m. in London.  
          
          


  


        